profile:
Bolder Contracting is a n excavation/roadbuilding company specializing in all aspects of excavation and wall building.
We welcome small, large, residential and commercial projects.
No job too big or too small.

Owner, Steve Skorey, uses his passion, talent and determination to stand out with exceptionally creative work.
